2414
01:42:56.300 --> 01:42:58.234
I'm coming.

2415
01:42:59.836 --> 01:43:02.100
Okay.

2416
01:43:03.173 --> 01:43:04.834
Okay, so that's going to be...

2417
01:43:04.875 --> 01:43:06.968
Michelle?

2418
01:43:09.046 --> 01:43:11.139
Andie...

2419
01:43:11.181 --> 01:43:12.614
that wasn't the Chinese.

2420
01:43:12.649 --> 01:43:14.310
