2421
01:43:14.351 --> 01:43:15.477
Mike?!

2422
01:43:15.519 --> 01:43:17.350
Yeah, what do I do?
What do I do?

2423
01:43:17.387 --> 01:43:19.947
Talk to him.

2424
01:43:19.990 --> 01:43:22.083
Okay, okay.

2425
01:43:24.161 --> 01:43:25.458
Okay.

2426
01:43:28.599 --> 01:43:30.567
Mike?

2427
01:43:30.601 --> 01:43:31.898
Mike?!

2428
01:43:31.935 --> 01:43:34.301
Hi.

2429
01:43:34.338 --> 01:43:36.033
Hi.

2430
01:43:37.274 --> 01:43:40.300
So...

2431
01:43:40.344 --> 01:43:42.369
what are you doing here?

2432
01:43:42.412 --> 01:43:43.845
I don't know exactly.

2433
01:43:45.082 --> 01:43:47.744
It was last night...
I was...

2434
01:43:47.784 --> 01:43:50.981
I was just lying there
and trying to sleep, and...

2435
01:43:51.021 --> 01:43:55.014
you know that perfume
you sprayed on my pillow?

2436
01:43:55.125 --> 01:43:56.752
Oh, yeah.

2437
01:43:56.793 --> 01:43:59.193
Well, that smell is gone now,

2438
01:43:59.229 --> 01:44:01.129
and...

2439
01:44:01.164 --> 01:44:03.155
Michelle, I want it back.

2440
01:44:03.200 --> 01:44:05.259
I...

2441
01:44:06.803 --> 01:44:09.203
I don't know
if you can have it back.

2442
01:44:13.110 --> 01:44:15.374
Right.

2443
01:44:15.412 --> 01:44:16.640
Yeah.

2444
01:44:16.680 --> 01:44:17.942
Okay.

2445
01:44:20.450 --> 01:44:22.714
But I'm willing

2446
01:44:22.753 --> 01:44:24.914
to consider it.

2447
01:44:24.955 --> 01:44:26.616
Okay.

2448
01:44:26.657 --> 01:44:28.124
- Yeah.
- Oh, my...

2449
01:44:28.158 --> 01:44:29.853
These are for you.

2450
01:44:29.893 --> 01:44:30.985
Thank you.

2451
01:44:31.028 --> 01:44:32.586
Hi.

2452
01:44:32.629 --> 01:44:34.620
Hi.

2453
01:44:45.909 --> 01:44:47.877
We could kiss.

2454
01:44:47.911 --> 01:44:49.640
I remember where you live.

2455
01:44:53.750 --> 01:44:56.275
Who needs men?

2456
01:44:56.319 --> 01:45:02.952
Ladies... frost yourselves.

2457
01:45:05.729 --> 01:45:06.855
Beautiful.

2458
01:45:06.897 --> 01:45:07.921
And cut it.

2459
01:45:07.964 --> 01:45:09.192
Very nice.

2460
01:45:09.232 --> 01:45:10.199
You like?

2461
01:45:10.233 --> 01:45:11.200
Oh, it was superb.

2462
01:45:11.234 --> 01:45:12.428
Okay, let's go one more.

2463
01:45:12.469 --> 01:45:14.232
Right away, people.

2464
01:45:14.271 --> 01:45:16.068
Real good.
I'll keep working on it.

2465
01:45:16.106 --> 01:45:17.971
Tim, can I see playback?

2466
01:45:18.075 --> 01:45:19.201
Open me, Ben.

2467
01:45:19.242 --> 01:45:20.368
Please, break my binding.

2468
01:45:20.410 --> 01:45:21.672
- Jesus.
- Please.

2469
01:45:21.712 --> 01:45:23.111
- Get that out of here, man.
- Please?

2470
01:45:23.146 --> 01:45:24.636
Straightening this out.

2471
01:45:24.681 --> 01:45:25.909
You might want to read this.

2472
01:45:25.949 --> 01:45:27.814
Ah, no thanks.

2473
01:45:27.851 --> 01:45:29.716
Yeah?

2474
01:45:29.753 --> 01:45:32.551
I've lost a guy,
and I don't know why.

2475
01:45:32.589 --> 01:45:34.352
What went wrong?

2476
01:45:34.391 --> 01:45:36.621
When I started writing
this month's column,

2477
01:45:36.660 --> 01:45:39.527
I wanted to commit the certain
silly dating faux pas.

2478
01:45:39.563 --> 01:45:41.997
What I didn't realize was

2479
01:45:42.032 --> 01:45:44.000
that I was making
the biggest mistake...

2480
01:45:44.034 --> 01:45:45.296
of all.

2481
01:45:45.335 --> 01:45:48.998
Here. Trust me.

2482
01:45:49.072 --> 01:45:51.199
Read it.

2483
01:46:07.224 --> 01:46:09.215
Come on set.

2484
01:46:19.136 --> 01:46:21.127
Andie Anderson?

2485
01:46:31.682 --> 01:46:33.809
Excuse me, ma'am.

2486
01:46:33.850 --> 01:46:34.976
Holy crap.

2487
01:46:35.085 --> 01:46:36.211
Where's Andie Anderson?

2488
01:46:36.253 --> 01:46:37.242
She's not here.

2489
01:46:37.287 --> 01:46:38.584
- Where is she?
- She quit.

2490
01:46:38.622 --> 01:46:40.214
She's got an interview
in Washington.

2491
01:46:40.257 --> 01:46:41.087
When is she leaving?

2492
01:46:41.124 --> 01:46:42.250
- Today.
- When?

2493
01:46:42.292 --> 01:46:44.852
Well, like, now.

2494
01:46:47.264 --> 01:46:49.164
You're not a therapist, are you?

2495
01:46:50.334 --> 01:46:51.358
No.

2496
01:46:51.401 --> 01:46:52.493
Good job, though.

2497
01:46:55.772 --> 01:46:57.706
You owe me 300 bucks.

2498
01:47:16.059 --> 01:47:17.117
Andy!

2499
01:47:46.890 --> 01:47:48.323
Hey!

2500
01:48:24.061 --> 01:48:25.221
Andy!

2501
01:48:26.430 --> 01:48:27.419
Ben!

2502
01:48:27.464 --> 01:48:29.523
Pull over, we need to talk.

2503
01:48:29.566 --> 01:48:32.660
Are you trying
to get yourself killed?

2504
01:48:32.703 --> 01:48:34.102
If that's what it takes, yeah.

2505
01:48:34.137 --> 01:48:35.161
Now pull over the cab.

2506
01:48:35.205 --> 01:48:36.968
Sir...

2507
01:48:37.040 --> 01:48:37.972
Excuse me, sir.

2508
01:48:38.041 --> 01:48:39.133
Can you please pull
the car over?

2509
01:48:39.176 --> 01:48:41.610
We're in the middle of a bridge,
lady.

2510
01:48:41.645 --> 01:48:42.737
I can't pull the car over here.

2511
01:48:42.779 --> 01:48:44.337
Okay, well, do you have
an ashtray

2512
01:48:44.381 --> 01:48:45.814
or something I can throw up in?

2513
01:48:45.849 --> 01:48:46.838
Gee, lady.

2514
01:48:52.923 --> 01:48:54.322
Watch it, broad!

2515
01:48:54.357 --> 01:48:55.688
What the hell was that?

2516
01:48:55.726 --> 01:48:57.216
Is this true?

2517
01:48:58.695 --> 01:48:59.662
Ben, please.

2518
01:48:59.696 --> 01:49:00.685
Is this true?

2519
01:49:00.731 --> 01:49:03.723
Or are you just trying
to sell magazines?

2520
01:49:07.104 --> 01:49:09.538
I meant every word.

2521
01:49:11.074 --> 01:49:13.235
Well, where you going?

2522
01:49:14.344 --> 01:49:15.936
I have an interview.

2523
01:49:16.012 --> 01:49:17.343
Yeah, in Washington.

2524
01:49:17.380 --> 01:49:18.711
I know.

2525
01:49:22.319 --> 01:49:24.480
Where you going?

2526
01:49:26.156 --> 01:49:28.147
Ben, it's the only place
I can go

2527
01:49:28.191 --> 01:49:29.818
and write what I want to write.

2528
01:49:30.894 --> 01:49:33.089
No, I'm not buying that.

2529
01:49:33.130 --> 01:49:36.099
You can write anywhere.

2530
01:49:37.467 --> 01:49:39.435
I think you're running away.

2531
01:49:39.469 --> 01:49:42.563
Why don't you save your mind
games for your next bet, okay?

2532
01:49:42.606 --> 01:49:44.096
I am not running away.

2533
01:49:46.543 --> 01:49:48.010
Bullshit.

2534
01:49:55.752 --> 01:49:57.454
Excuse me?

2535
01:50:00.190 --> 01:50:01.657
You heard me.

2536
01:50:04.961 --> 01:50:06.519
Bullshit.

2537
01:50:08.264 --> 01:50:11.358
Hey, lady, what do ya wanna do?

2538
01:50:12.869 --> 01:50:13.858
Take the lady's luggage

2539
01:50:13.903 --> 01:50:15.131
back to her place.

2540
01:50:15.171 --> 01:50:17.503
She has alternate
transportation.

2541
01:50:20.343 --> 01:50:22.971
You callin' my bluff?

2542
01:50:23.012 --> 01:50:25.139
You bet I am.

2543
01:50:44.033 --> 01:50:46.024
Look who made the trip with me.

2544
01:50:46.135 --> 01:50:48.228
It's our love fern.

2545
01:50:48.271 --> 01:50:49.966
Oh, Benny-boo-boo,
boo-boo-boo.
